{"tid":660004,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"金球獎影后加盟《驚奇隊長》","createTime":"2018-05-10T10:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T05:49:10.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"414c5933e42255a39f6467b2cedf4687d92088db","tid":660004,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:26:41.000Z","msg":"《驚奇隊長（Captain Marvel）》再添新卡司，金球獎影后安妮特&middot;貝南（Annette Bening）宣布加盟。<br />\n<br />\n據外媒報導，貝南將首度參演超級英雄電影，飾演一位科學家角色，目前片方暫未透露她的角色細節。<br />\n<br />\n《驚奇隊長》由布麗&middot;拉爾森（Brie Larson）領銜主演，塞繆爾&middot;傑克遜（Samuel L. Jackson）、本&middot;門德爾森（Ben Mendelsohn）、Lashana Lynch、嘉瑪&middot;陳（Gemma Chan）、Algenis Perez Soto、Rune Temte、麥肯娜&middot;格瑞絲（McKenna Grace）以及裘德&middot;洛（Jude Law）共同主演。<br />\n<br />\n安妮特&middot;貝南早在1992年就曾擬在《蝙蝠俠歸來（ Batman Returns）》中飾演貓女，但後來因懷孕而遺憾退出。此後接任這一角色的是米歇爾&middot;菲佛（Michelle Pfeiffer），值得一提的是，後者目前也參演了MCU影片，在《蟻人2：黃蜂女現身（Ant-Man and the Wasp）》中飾演珍妮特&middot;范&middot;戴因（Janet Van Dyne）。"},{"pid":"7cb5698e3ca6a43e7031e0a1fd21826409ebe3f8","tid":660004,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:20:13.000Z","msg":"唔好做歹多唔係又一集棄"},{"pid":"5bc5c2b3ca838082e76d771fd7fd5e1e31b0b469","tid":660004,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:20:57.000Z","msg":"hello moto"},{"pid":"a74c336550cb26f8daf33bd1158358820ceb32b8","tid":660004,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bc5c2b3ca838082e76d771fd7fd5e1e31b0b469","tid":660004,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:20:57.000Z","msg":"hello moto"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce10eeec986beca346f2fe7ef7c7a0460f1eeec","tid":660004,"uid":160555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"Gemma Chan<img src=\"/assets/faces/no